headLine: Code Queens Chanllenge
textContext: Code Queens programming contest is only for Girls in our CSE department. It's a great opportunity to showcase your skills and be a part of a community of girls who are passionate about programming. We encourage all the girls to join and show us what you have. Hope everyone joins and have a great time!
